In commemoration of Women’s  Month, the Christian Revival  Centre Sister’s  Department held an empowering conference called  “Dancing in the Rain”. The aim was to teach women how to overcome the storms of life with joy and strength from God. Praise and worship was enjoyed with international guest speaker, Dr Edith Prakash, daughter of Sister Padma Moodliar of India, who strongly believes in healing, deliverance and evangelism.  All ladies in attendance were inspired and pampered at the event.